        <p><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Context string </span>When using context-sensitive (F1) and dynamic Help with Microsoft Help 2.0, this option specifies the context string for the topic. Each topic can have one or more context strings, or none. The context strings must be separated by a semicolon. Topic context strings form a hierarchical tree structure. A context string consists of dot-separated context names for each hierarchy level.</p>
